{
  "stem": "5248.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, part of Poland was annexed to Germany, like Lodz and-- and [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Parmadanya. ?] They were the old-- actually, when the old German profession, before the World War I, stayed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So Maybe Lwow-- Lwow ghetto, maybe, had less people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, they collected people from the provincial cities and pulled them all in one place to make it easier for them So there were many people in ghetto who did not have means to buy food or anything else.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were still lucky with our possession.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's how it-- we survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, once you went to work so you were gone during the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, at night everybody was equally frightened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had-- as I mentioned before, we had to leave my brother in the ghetto, and that was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although he managed, somehow, to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, people got together and they would tell-- and somehow the-- actually there was no mail, no services, but the news would come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, all the killing took place during the daytime, but people would get-- talk about--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at this point I think it was pre-determined, but also several killings at random.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was some stealing going on, and they hung several policemen just at random to--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but I don't think they had anything much to do with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Example, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there was a Judenrat, and the police-- and-- well, they were the main forces.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Judenrat would give people those cards that they have-- that they have a job, so they should be excluded, or they have a profession which might be useful to Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In many cases it did, but sometimes you had to-- they saw-- there were also Ukrainian police-- policemen guarding the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
